article.headline: Andrews leads Alcorn St. past Our Lady of the Lake 92-56
article.linkText: Andrews leads Alcorn St. past Our Lady of the Lake 92-56
article.story: LORMAN, Miss. -- Deshaw Andrews had 20 points and grabbed eight rebounds as Alcorn State routed NAIA-member Our Lady of the Lake 92-56 on Thursday. Corey Tillery had 14 points for Alcorn State (2-4) in the first-ever meeting of the teams. Maurice Howard added 12 points and Troymain Crosby had six rebounds. Jared Embry had 18 points for the Saints. Finn Wilczek added 12 points. Alcorn State takes on Arkansas-Little Rock on the road on Wednesday. --- For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/Collegebasketball and http://twitter.com/AP-Top25 --- Elements of this story were generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
